{"uuid":"recommended65250","createDate":1568840820000,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"65250\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 12:22:58\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2019-09-19\",\"gameName\":\"Train Simulator: BR Class 76 &amp; 77 Loco Add-On\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/65250\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/65250/\",\"playTime\":\"0.0\",\"updateTime\":\"2019-09-19\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"0.0\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/65250\"}","type":"steamReview","title":"评测 > Train Simulator: BR Class 76 &amp; 77 Loco Add-On","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n 模拟火车：BR Class 76和 77机车组DLC~\n <br>\n 包含了2类电力机车，BR Class 76、BR Class 77，而且有职业任务\n <br>\n 但是职业任务需要Woodhead线路~~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/65244/Train_Simulator_Woodhead_Route_AddOn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/65244/Train_Simulator_Woodhead_Route_AddOn/</a>\n <br>\n 我又没有这个DLC~太好了~省钱省时间了~啊哈哈~\n <br>\n <br>\n 这2列机车组估计是太过于相像了~所以才合并到一个DLC~\n <br>\n 作为早期的电力机车，车头还是比较粗犷简洁的，比如车头副驾驶那大大的手刹阀门，\n <br>\n 喇叭带有2段回音；Class77的节流阀和反向器都很粗犷，一块大铁块的感觉~\n <br>\n 76就感觉好原始~还有各种手动刹车阀~\n <br>\n 雨刷开关也很有特色、是个阀门\n <br>\n 而且开车前记得把导电弓挂上，虽然我在驾驶室中肿么都没找到导电弓的开关，还好有HUD！\n <br>\n 而且这车的刹车有3种以上，HUD最多支持3种刹车！于是多了的只能在驾驶室里自己点了~\n <br>\n <br>\n BR Class 76时速表最高才75mph~最快也就62左右~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1867034849\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1867034849</a>\n <br>\n <br>\n BR Class 77时速表最高才120mph~最快也就111左右~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1867030756\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_2\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1867030756</a>\n <br>\n <br>\n 毕竟是电力机车，运行起来除了风噪外，发动机的声音真的很小很小~\n <br>\n 遮阳板、雨刷开关、室内灯光、车灯、仪表灯光控制都模拟到了~\n <br>\n 唯独找不到导电弓的开关~emm~\n</div>\n<div id=\"ReviewEdit\" style=\"display: none\">\n <textarea id=\"ReviewEditTextArea\" class=\"review_edit_text_area\" maxlength=\"8000\" rows=\"2\" cols=\"80\">模拟火车：BR Class 76和 77机车组DLC~\n包含了2类电力机车，BR Class 76、BR Class 77，而且有职业任务\n但是职业任务需要Woodhead线路~~\nhttps://store.steampowered.com/app/65244/Train_Simulator_Woodhead_Route_AddOn/\n我又没有这个DLC~太好了~省钱省时间了~啊哈哈~\n\n这2列机车组估计是太过于相像了~所以才合并到一个DLC~\n作为早期的电力机车，车头还是比较粗犷简洁的，比如车头副驾驶那大大的手刹阀门，\n喇叭带有2段回音；Class77的节流阀和反向器都很粗犷，一块大铁块的感觉~\n76就感觉好原始~还有各种手动刹车阀~\n雨刷开关也很有特色、是个阀门\n而且开车前记得把导电弓挂上，虽然我在驾驶室中肿么都没找到导电弓的开关，还好有HUD！\n而且这车的刹车有3种以上，HUD最多支持3种刹车！于是多了的只能在驾驶室里自己点了~\n\nBR Class 76时速表最高才75mph~最快也就62左右~\nhttps://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1867034849\n\nBR Class 77时速表最高才120mph~最快也就111左右~\nhttps://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1867030756\n\n毕竟是电力机车，运行起来除了风噪外，发动机的声音真的很小很小~\n遮阳板、雨刷开关、室内灯光、车灯、仪表灯光控制都模拟到了~\n唯独找不到导电弓的开关~emm~</textarea>\n <div class=\"review_edit_received_compensation\">\n  <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ReceivedCompensationCheckbox\" value=\"1\"> <label for=\"ReceivedCompensationCheckbox\">如果您是免费获取的此产品，请勾选此框 <a data-tooltip-text=\"如果您是免费获取的此产品，请勾选此框。您的评测旁会显示“免费获取的产品”。如果您评测此游戏还收到了其他报酬，必须在您的评测文本中披露。\">(?)</a></label>\n </div>\n <div style=\"float: left\">\n  您推荐这款游戏吗？ <span class=\"btnv6_blue_hoverfade btn_small_thin ico_hover active\" onclick=\"SetOwnerRatingPositive();\" id=\"OwnerVoteUpBtn\"> <span><i class=\"ico16 thumb_up\"></i> 是</span> </span> <span class=\"btnv6_blue_hoverfade btn_small_thin ico_hover \" onclick=\"SetOwnerRatingNegative();\" id=\"OwnerVoteDownBtn\"> <span><i class=\"ico16 thumb_down\"></i>否</span> </span>\n </div>\n <div style=\"float: right\">\n  <span class=\"btn_small_thin btn_grey_white_innerfade\" onclick=\"CancelEdits();\" id=\"CancelEditsBtn\"> <span>取消</span> </span> <span class=\"btn_small_thin btn_blue_white_innerfade\" onclick=\"SaveReview();\" id=\"SaveReviewBtn\"> <span>保存修改</span> </span>\n </div>\n <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>